Package org.cytoscape.cyGraph.algorithms.api

This package provides access to various graph algorithms.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BellmanFordResult Provides methods to get the shortest path, distance, etc.
BfsResult Provides methods to get the shortest path and distance from source CyNode to other CyNodes computed by breadth first search.
Callback Callback function to be provided by the user.
DfsResult Provides methods to get the path from source CyNode to other CyNodes as computed depth first search
DijkstraResult Provides methods to access get shortest path from source CyNode to other CyNodes, distance, etc.
FloydWarshallResult Provides methods to get shortest path between a given pair of nodes, negative cycle if one exists, etc.
GraphAlgorithms GraphAlgorithms is the primary interface providing access to a number of graph algorithms.
HITSResults Provides methods to get the hub and authority value of a CyNode as computed by HITS.
MSTResult Provides methods to get the weight of the minimum spanning tree and the minimum spanning tree itself.
PagerankResults Provides method to get the pagerank value of a node.
WeightFunction WeightFunction i.e.
